  <p>As of AEM 6.1 Communities, a blog is a community activity. Blog articles are now posted from the publish environment, where previously, blog articles could only be created in the author environment and published .</p> 
  <p>Blog articles may now be created by any community member, unless restricted to privileged members.</p> 
  <p>This page provides the essential information for working with the blog feature.</p> 
  <note>
   <p>The underlying infrastructure of the blog feature is the journal feature.</p> 
  </note>
  <h2>Essentials for Client-Side</h2>
  <p>The blog feature is comprised of two main components that are available by adding the <a href="../../communities/using/functions.md#blogfunction">Blog function</a> or by adding the components to a page in author edit mode.</p> 
